SunSpec Alliance Model Definitions
Device profiles that map SunSpec models (for example
solar-inverter/fronius-gen24) reference SunSpec register model identifiers
and field names derived from the SunSpec Alliance public model
specifications (https://sunspec.org). These are independent ModDef mappings
and are not endorsed by or affiliated with the SunSpec Alliance.
